title: What's In A Name?
description:
Trenni Kusnierek is now Trenni Casey, which has sparked a new reality show idea (00:05:00). Craig Carton says he turned down being groomed to coach in the NFL by Bill Belichick (00:36:00). Maitland Ward joins us to discuss her new book, "Rated X: How Porn Liberated Me from Hollywood" (00:40:00). Brendan Fraser is receiving rave reviews for his new movie but some people are upset a fat person didn't play a fat character, calls & much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
